IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Jane M. FRICK and Duane T. Frick, Jr. Upon the Petition of Jane M. Frick, Petitioner-Appellee, And Concerning Duane T. Frick, Jr., Respondent-Appellant. No. 17-1334 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 23, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Duane Frick challenges the economic provisions arising out of the dissolution of his marriage. AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED.

AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED.
